These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: azure, lavender, light-blue, blue, ebony
The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, skateboard, van, snowmobile, taxi
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, july, november, february, august
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, lacrosse, skiing, swimming
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 2. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who likes ebony##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is the person who likes lavender##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
 9. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
10. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
11. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's sport is baseball##1
12. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Color         | lavender  | azure    | blue | light-blue    | ebony  |
| Transport   | skateboard  | jet-ski | van | snowmobile | taxi  |
| Birthday           | october     | august     | february  | july   | november    |
| Sport         | lacrosse | skiing    | cycling | baseball  | swimming |

