.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: green, purple, blood-red, grey, lavender
The people have 5 different jobs:  accountant, architect, dressmaker, photographer, scientist
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, september, november, may, march
The people have 5 different hobbies: writing, card-games, reading, cooking, chess
 1. the photographer is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 6. the dressmaker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the scientist is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the person who likes blood-red is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 9. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who likes blood-red##1
10. the person who likes purple is in the middle##1
11. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the person who likes blood-red is the architect##1
13. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Color          | blood-red        | lavender | purple     | grey      | green  |
| Job           | architect   | dressmaker | scientist    | photographer | accountant |
| Birthday   | november | may     | march | february    | september  |
| Hobby   | cooking     | card-games | writing    | chess      | reading    |

