.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
House: victorian, art-deco, ranch-style, townhouse, colonial
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, reading, traveling, writing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: zombie, martial-arts, comedy, action, epic
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: weightlifting, handball, baseball, rowing, sailing
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1
 4. the art-deco house is in the middle##1
 5. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 8. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 9. the person who's sport is sailing is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
12. the colonial house is on the right of the victorian house##1
13. the townhouse house is the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| House      | townhouse          | ranch-style  | art-deco       | victorian     | colonial      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | writing | traveling  | reading   | cooking    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts        | epic | zombie | action    | comedy   |
| Sport     | weightlifting   | baseball | sailing      | handball | rowing |

