.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: daisy, aconite, azalea, poppy, iris
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, horror, scientific, superhero, time-travel
5 different pets are kept: snake, cat, bird, rat, turtle
There are 5 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, sprite, juice, tea
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 3. the owner of the cat is the person watching horror movies##1
 4. the owner of the snake is the person watching drama movies##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 7. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 8. the person drinking tea is in the middle##1
 9. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
10. the person who growsiris is the owner of the bird##1
11. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
12. the person drinking milk is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Flower          | poppy        | daisy       | azalea | aconite   | iris  |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | scientific | horror | drama   | superhero |
| Pet   | rat         | turtle     | cat | snake | bird     |
| Beverage     | milk        | mirinda        | tea    | juice    | sprite      |

