 1. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is the mechanic##1
 3. the security-guard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 6. the designer is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the photographer##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
| Transport          | bike    | trike  | motorbike | train    | helicopter      |
