.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: soul, metal, house, country, trance
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: comedy, epic, fantasy, scientific, sports
There 5 different types of food: pear, onion, peach, lemon, avocado
House: cape-cod, modern, art-deco, gothic-revival, victorian
 1. the person watching comedy movies is the victorian house##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 3. the person eating pear is on the far right##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 5. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
 7. the person watching scientific movies is the art-deco house##1
 8. the gothic-revival house is the person eating lemon##1
 9. the fan of house is on the far left##1
10. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
11. the fan of soul is in the middle##1
12. the gothic-revival house is the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |     3      |     4     |       5       |
| Music-Genre         | house  | trance  | soul    | metal | country |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy        | fantasy  | scientific | epic      | sports        |
| Food   | onion       | lemon  | peach   | avocado | pear     |
| House         | victorian | gothic-revival | art-deco | modern  | cape-cod      |

