The people prefer 5 different music-genres: salsa, trance, techno, soul, ambient
5 different pets are kept: snake, ferret, hedgehog, chinchilla, goat
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, boat, train, tram, trike
 1. the fan of ambient is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 2. the person driving the train is the fan of techno##1
 3. the dannemann-smoker is in the middle##1
 4. the fan of salsa is the owner of the snake##1
 5. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is in the middle##1
 8. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 9. the person driving the boat is on the left of the fan of trance##1
10. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
11. the fan of salsa is the oliveros-smoker##1
12. the person driving the tram is the owner of the ferret##1
13. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |     5     |
| Cigar          | oliveros     | ritmeester  | dannemann | bolivar     | old-henry |
| Music-Genre           | salsa   | trance | ambient     | techno | soul |
| Pet   | snake | ferret  | hedgehog     | chinchilla   | goat    |
| Transport     | boat       | tram     | trike     | train      | airplane  |

