The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, musical, spy, documentary
The people have 5 different jobs:  freelancer, doctor, electrician, project-manager, firefighter
 1. the freelancer is the fan of rock##1
 2. the fan of jazz is on the right of the american##1
 3. the freelancer is on the far left##1
 4. the german is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of punk##1
 6. the fan of punk is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 7. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
 8. the doctor is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
 9. the german is the electrician##1
10. the turkish is in the middle##1
11. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the turkish##1
12. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
13. the fan of punk is on the left of the electrician##1
14. the firefighter is on the left of the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |       4       |    5     |
