 3. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 5. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 6. the tiparillo-smoker is the person watching documentary movies##1
