10. the dannemann-smoker is the person drinking juice##1
11. the person who's birthday is in march is the person watching scientific movies##1
12. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
13. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
