10. the person who likes purple is the person who growsazalea##1
11. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1
12. the person who growssunflower is the person who likes pink##1
13. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |    4    |    5    |
