.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, juice, milk
There 5 different types of food: banana, tomato, pepper, pear, radish
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skiing, climbing, water-polo, surfing, ice-hockey
