 1. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
 3. the person eating pear is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 4. the pilot is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 5. the person eating banana is on the left of the accountant##1
 6. the librarian is on the right of the pilot##1
 7. the person eating tomato is the musician##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 9. the accountant is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
10. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
11. the bartender is on the left of the person eating radish##1
12. the person eating pepper is the person who's sport is surfing##1
13. the person eating radish is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola       | milk         | juice  | iced-tea |
| Food   | pepper  | pear | tomato | banana  | radish  |
| Sport   | surfing    | climbing    | skiing        | ice-hockey | water-polo     |
| Job           | pilot | librarian      | musician       | bartender   | accountant   |

