.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda, sprite
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, may, january, december, april
5 different pets are kept: horse, rat, snake, goat, guinea-pig
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, orchid, lily, aconite, begonia
 1. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 5. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
 6. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is the owner of the rat##1
 8. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
12. the person who's birthday is in april is in the middle##1
13. the owner of the horse is the person drinking mirinda##1
14. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
